OL,3,CSouthern bus route reinstated in Isle
OL,4,Cof Man following public outcry
OL,6,FCampaigners say they are 'relieved'
OL,7,Ffollowing the reinstatement of a bus
OL,8,Froute serving people living in the
OL,9,Fsouthernmost point of the Isle of Man.
OL,11,FChrista Viohl, founder of the 'Save
OL,12,Four Cregneash Bus' group, hailed the
OL,13,F'winning situation', saying that
OL,14,F'grassroots power finally succeeded',
OL,15,Fand 'many people should profit from
OL,16,Fthis solution'.
OL,18,FShe added that residents 'now have the
OL,19,Fopportunity to get out of their
OL,20,Fhouses', after being reliant on family
OL,21,Fand friends to travel.
