OL,3,CSouthern bus route reinstated in Isle
OL,4,Cof Man following public outcry
OL,6,FResidents and businesses along the
OL,7,Froute had previously said they felt
OL,8,F'stranded' without a bus route
OL,9,Fconnecting them to the rest of the
OL,10,Fisland.
OL,12,FThe service was previously scrapped in
OL,13,Fthe summer of 2023, after the
OL,14,Fgovernment deemed it to be 'not
OL,15,Ffinancially viable'.
OL,17,FHowever the decision has been made to
OL,18,Freintroduce a bus service to the
OL,19,FSound, this time via a different route
OL,20,Falso connecting to the west of the
OL,21,FIsle of Man.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
