OL,3,CSouthern bus route reinstated in Isle
OL,4,Cof Man following public outcry
OL,6,FBus Vannin say the 8S service will
OL,7,Fconnect Peel, Foxdale, Ronaldsway
OL,8,FAirport, Castletown, Port Erin (via
OL,9,FShore Road), Port St Mary and the
OL,10,FSound via Cregneash.
OL,12,FThe government say they hope the route
OL,13,Fwill start operating in time for the
OL,14,Fschool summer holidays, and will run
OL,15,Fall year round, seven days a week.
OL,17,FThis will be subject to approval from
OL,18,Fthe Road Transport Licensing Committee.
