OL,3,CSouthern bus route reinstated in Isle
OL,4,Cof Man following public outcry
OL,6,FInfrastructure Minister Dr Michelle
OL,7,FHaywood said: 'I am delighted that Bus
OL,8,FVannin are able to introduce this
OL,9,Froute. Connecting the west of the
OL,10,FIsland and Foxdale directly to the
OL,11,Fairport and onwards to Cregneash and
OL,12,Fthe Sound is good news for residents
OL,13,Fand visitors to our Island.'
OL,15,FChrista concluded by saying: "We will
OL,16,Fkeep a close eye on further
OL,17,Fdevelopments, ready to call out again
OL,18,Fif necessary.
