OL,3,CSouthern bus route reinstated in Isle
OL,4,Cof Man following public outcry
OL,6,F"We now need proper advertising for
OL,7,Fthe bus to let everybody know it will
OL,8,Fbe back again. We need impressive
OL,9,Fpassenger numbers to keep it.
OL,11,F"This will not be easy during winter
OL,12,Fwhen the weather is not ideal for
OL,13,Fhaving a day out and when the number
OL,14,Fof tourists is low. Please do not let
OL,15,Fbad weather stop you from using the
OL,16,Fbus."
